---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../../../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import { t } from '../../../i18n/utils';

const locale = 'en';
const i = t(locale);
---

<Base
  nav="light"
  title="Couples therapy with a relational approach | Mexico City & online"
  description="Support for couples: communication, bonding and conflict from a relational and somatic-based approach. In-person sessions in Mexico City and online."
  altPath="/terapia/pareja/"
  ogImage="/uploads/og/therapy-couples.webp"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <SiteHeader
    variant="panel"
    eyebrow="Couples therapy"
    icon="/uploads/icono-terapia-pareja.webp"
    iconSize="132px"
    title="A safe space to reconnect with your life partner."
    ctaLabel="Book your first couples session"
    ctaHref="https://wa.me/patriciomx?text=Hi%20Patricio%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20scheduling%20a%20first%20couples%20session.%20Can%20we%20talk%3F"
    secondaryLabel="What is the first session like?"
    secondaryHref="#primera-sesion"
  >
    <p>For couples caught in the same arguments, who've grown apart, or who are working to rebuild broken trust to reconnect.</p>
    <p>Dating relationships, domestic partnerships and marriages · Nápoles, Mexico City &amp; online</p>
  </SiteHeader>

  <!-- IS THIS FOR YOU? -->
  <section style="padding:clamp(64px,9vw,116px) 32px;background:var(--cream-2);">
    <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
      <p data-reveal class="label-section">Indications</p>
      <h2 data-reveal class="heading-section" style="margin-bottom:40px;">Is this therapy right for you?</h2>
      <div class="two-col" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px;">
        <div data-reveal style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:34px 32px;">
          <p style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple);margin:0 0 20px;">It is for you if...</p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:13px;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">✓</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">You want to strengthen your relationship before a major step: marriage, children, moving in together.</p></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">✓</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">The arrival or departure of children changed your dynamic and you can't find a way to reconnect or redefine yourselves.</p></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">✓</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">You keep having the same arguments over and over and can't find a way out.</p></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">✓</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">You feel emotionally distant: you're together but disconnected.</p></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">✓</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">Something happened that broke your trust and you can't find a way to repair or move forward.</p></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--purple);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">✓</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">You're considering separating and want to bring closure under the best possible conditions.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:34px 32px;">
          <p style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--wine);margin:0 0 20px;">It is not for you if...</p>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:13px;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--wine);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">–</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">You need legal mediation, arbitration or divorce management. I can point you to the right resource.</p></div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;"><span style="color:var(--wine);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;flex:none;line-height:1.4;">–</span><p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3a36;">There is active, recurring physical or psychological violence of a structural nature.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW WE WORK -->
  <section style="padding:clamp(64px,9vw,116px) 32px;">
    <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
      <p data-reveal class="label-section">The process</p>
      <h2 data-reveal class="heading-section" style="margin-bottom:28px;">Rhythm, depth and method</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;">
        <p data-reveal class="body-text" style="margin:0;">In the first session I carry out an assessment by exploring the couple's history with both of you. I take the side of what I believe can support the relationship: I work with it as a third entity -- something that belongs to and is the responsibility of both, and that with support and commitment can transform for the benefit of both.</p>
        <p data-reveal class="body-text" style="margin:0;">We weave a conversation where the goal is not to convince the other person whose pain matters more, but to understand how the couple is hurting from the way it is functioning, and what each partner can do to tend to and repair the friction in the bond.</p>
        <p data-reveal class="body-text" style="margin:0;">Sessions are typically biweekly, lasting approximately one hour. During times of crisis we can consider weekly sessions. We can meet in person in Napoles or online with the same depth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3 TRANSFORMATIONS -->
  <section style="padding:clamp(64px,9vw,116px) 32px;background:var(--cream-2);">
    <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:clamp(40px,5vw,60px);">
        <p data-reveal class="label-section">Evolution</p>
        <h2 data-reveal class="heading-section">What changes as the process unfolds</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(min(280px,100%),1fr));gap:24px;">
        <div data-reveal style="background:#fff;border-radius:22px;padding:36px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
          <span style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:48px;color:var(--cream);line-height:1;">1</span>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--wine);font-size:22px;margin:0;">From argument to relational listening</h3>
          <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#4a443f;margin:0;">Recurring arguments are not the problem -- they are the symptom. When you can name what is happening in your body in the moment of conflict, it becomes possible to interrupt the cycle.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal style="background:#fff;border-radius:22px;padding:36px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
          <span style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:48px;color:var(--cream);line-height:1;">2</span>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--wine);font-size:22px;margin:0;">A relationship that holds you</h3>
          <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#4a443f;margin:0;">The shared vocabulary, the tools to navigate conflict and the trust that you can get through hard things together -- you take all of that with you. The relationship as refuge, resource and safe place.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal style="background:#fff;border-radius:22px;padding:36px 30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
          <span style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:48px;color:var(--cream);line-height:1;">3</span>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--wine);font-size:22px;margin:0;">Recovering intimacy</h3>
          <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#4a443f;margin:0;">Emotional distance is built through small disconnections. As the process unfolds, you begin to recognize each other again: knowing what hurts, what provides security, what you need -- and asking for it without falling into an endless argument.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FIRST SESSION + COST -->
  <section id="primera-sesion" style="padding:clamp(64px,9vw,116px) 32px;">
    <div class="two-col" style="max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:40px;align-items:start;">
      <div>
        <p data-reveal class="label-section">Your first session</p>
        <h2 data-reveal style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--purple);font-size:clamp(26px,3.5vw,40px);line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 28px;">Step by step</h2>
        <div data-reveal style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;padding-bottom:22px;">
            <div style="flex:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;"><span style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--purple);color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex:none;">1</span><span style="flex:1;width:2px;background:var(--cream);min-height:20px;margin-top:6px;"></span></div>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:#3f3a36;padding-top:5px;">One of you reaches out via WhatsApp. We clarify any questions about scheduling and payment. Confirmation 48 hours in advance.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;padding-bottom:22px;">
            <div style="flex:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;"><span style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--purple);color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex:none;">2</span><span style="flex:1;width:2px;background:var(--cream);min-height:20px;margin-top:6px;"></span></div>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:#3f3a36;padding-top:5px;">The first session is a mutual interview. We define what you expect from the process and set realistic expectations.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;padding-bottom:22px;">
            <div style="flex:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;"><span style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--purple);color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex:none;">3</span><span style="flex:1;width:2px;background:var(--cream);min-height:20px;margin-top:6px;"></span></div>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:#3f3a36;padding-top:5px;">The first 3 to 6 sessions are an adjustment period: we calibrate how the space feels for each of you.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;">
            <span style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--purple);color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex:none;">4</span>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65;color:#3f3a36;padding-top:5px;">We schedule in two-month periods with clear goals and constantly recalibrate progress.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal>
        <div style="background:var(--purple);border-radius:22px;padding:36px 32px;color:#fff;text-align:center;margin-bottom:22px;">
          <p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">Costs</p>
          <p style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(21px,2.3vw,26px);color:#fff;margin:0 0 12px;line-height:1.18;">Individual, couples, and family: same cost</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 22px;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);line-height:1.6;">Sessions of 50 to 60 minutes. See the per-session price and the continuity pack.</p>
          <a href="/en/costs/" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#fff;color:var(--purple);font-weight:700;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:99px;text-decoration:none;">See the costs</a>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;">
          <div style="background:var(--cream-2);border-radius:18px;padding:22px 24px;">
            <div style="font-family:'Mulish',sans-serif;font-size:38px;line-height:.6;color:var(--sand);margin-bottom:8px;">"</div>
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#34302c;margin:0 0 10px;">We learned to communicate better, to feel confident expressing our differences in a respectful way.</p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--purple);font-size:15px;">M + R</p>
          </div>
          <div style="background:var(--cream-2);border-radius:18px;padding:22px 24px;">
            <div style="font-family:'Mulish',sans-serif;font-size:38px;line-height:.6;color:var(--sand);margin-bottom:8px;">"</div>
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#34302c;margin:0 0 10px;">Patricio always supported us and created a wonderfully harmonious environment where we could open up and talk with respect.</p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--purple);font-size:15px;">Nay</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TECHNIQUES -->
  <section style="padding:clamp(64px,9vw,116px) 32px;background:var(--purple);">
    <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:clamp(40px,5vw,56px);">
        <p data-reveal style="margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sand);">Approaches</p>
        <h2 data-reveal style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,46px);line-height:1.1;margin:0;">How I work in session</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(min(240px,100%),1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div data-reveal style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 24px;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--sand);font-size:17px;margin:0 0 10px;">Systemic Family Therapy</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin:0;">The backbone of my relational work. It focuses on interactions as the visible expression of the bond's health. It integrates resources from Gottman, Sue Johnson's Emotionally Focused Therapy and postmodern models.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 24px;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--sand);font-size:17px;margin:0 0 10px;">Somatic Experiencing (SE)</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin:0;">It pays attention to the nervous system responses of each partner and the dynamic between you. It helps regulate what the body holds before it can be processed with words.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 24px;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--sand);font-size:17px;margin:0 0 10px;">IFS -- Internal Family Systems</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin:0;">It works with the internal "parts" each partner brings to the relationship. When each person recognizes their parts, they stop projecting them onto the other.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 24px;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--sand);font-size:17px;margin:0 0 10px;">Core Energetics / Exceptional Marriage</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin:0;">A couples model derived from Core Energetics. It works with the body, emotions and relational patterns to facilitate free self-expression in a context of connection and safety.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA + CROSS-SELL -->
  <section style="padding:clamp(64px,9vw,112px) 32px;background:var(--cream-2);text-align:center;">
    <div data-reveal style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Bitter',serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--purple);font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,48px);line-height:1.08;margin:0 0 20px;text-wrap:balance;">Ready to book your first session?</h2>
      <a href="https://wa.me/patriciomx?text=Hi%20Patricio%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20scheduling%20a%20first%20couples%20session.%20Can%20we%20talk%3F" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">Book your first couples session</a>
      <p style="margin:30px 0 10px;color:#6a6460;font-size:15px;">Thinking about an individual process?</p>
      <a href="/en/therapy/individual/" style="color:var(--wine);font-weight:700;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;">Learn about my individual therapy</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
